{"id":470,"parent_id":454,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":470,"title":"Job 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"Job","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","Job speaks against the wicked who oppose him—Though even his friends scorn him, he testifies that his witness is in heaven and his record is on high."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.1","order":"02.19.016.33686"},["b","1"],"Then Job answered and said,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.2","order":"02.19.016.33687"},["b","2"],"I have heard many such things: miserable",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"comforters"],["i","are"],"ye all."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.3","order":"02.19.016.33688"},["b","3"],"Shall vain words have an end? or what emboldeneth thee that thou answerest?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.4","order":"02.19.016.33689"},["b","4"],"I also could speak as ye",["i","do:"],"if your soul were in my soul’s stead, I could heap up words against you, and shake mine head at you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.5","order":"02.19.016.33690"},["b","5"],["i","But"],"I would strengthen you with my mouth, and the moving of my lips should assuage",["i","your grief."]],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.6","order":"02.19.016.33691"},["b","6"],"Though I speak, my grief is not assuaged: and",["i","though"],"I forbear, what am I eased?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.7","order":"02.19.016.33692"},["b","7"],"But now he hath made me weary: thou hast made desolate all my company."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.8","order":"02.19.016.33693"},["b","8"],"And thou hast filled me with wrinkles,",["i","which"],"is a witness",["i","against me:"],"and my leanness rising up in me beareth witness to my face."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.9","order":"02.19.016.33694"},["b","9"],"He teareth",["i","me"],"in his wrath, who hateth me: he gnasheth upon me with his teeth; mine enemy sharpeneth his eyes upon me."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.10","order":"02.19.016.33695"},["b","10"],"They have gaped upon me with their mouth; they have smitten me upon the cheek",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"reproachfully"],"; they have gathered themselves together against me."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.11","order":"02.19.016.33696"},["b","11"],"God hath delivered me to the ungodly, and turned me over into the hands of the wicked."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.12","order":"02.19.016.33697"},["b","12"],"I was at ease, but he hath broken me asunder: he hath also taken",["i","me"],"by my neck, and shaken me to pieces, and set me up for his mark."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.13","order":"02.19.016.33698"},["b","13"],"His archers compass me round about, he cleaveth my reins asunder, and doth not spare; he poureth out my gall upon the ground."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.14","order":"02.19.016.33699"},["b","14"],"He breaketh me with breach upon breach, he runneth upon me like a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"giant"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.15","order":"02.19.016.33700"},["b","15"],"I have sewed sackcloth upon my skin, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"defiled my horn"],"in the dust."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.16","order":"02.19.016.33701"},["b","16"],"My face is foul with weeping, and on my eyelids",["i","is"],"the shadow of death;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.17","order":"02.19.016.33702"},["b","17"],"Not for",["i","any"],"injustice in mine hands: also my prayer",["i","is"],"pure."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.18","order":"02.19.016.33703"},["b","18"],"O earth, cover not thou my blood, and let my cry have no place."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.19","order":"02.19.016.33704"},["b","19"],"Also now, behold, my witness",["i","is"],"in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"heaven"],", and my record",["i","is"],"on high."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.20","order":"02.19.016.33705"},["b","20"],"My friends",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"scorn"],"me:",["i","but"],"mine eye poureth out",["i","tears"],"unto God."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.21","order":"02.19.016.33706"},["b","21"],"O that one might plead for a man with God, as a man",["i","pleadeth"],"for his neighbour!"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.22","order":"02.19.016.33707"},["b","22"],"When a few years are come, then I shall go the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"way"],["i","whence"],"I shall not return."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.2a","order":"02.19.016.33708"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/13.4"},"Job 13:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.10.7-11"},"D&C 121:10 (7–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.10a","order":"02.19.016.33710"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproach"},"TG Reproach"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.14a","order":"02.19.016.33712"},["b","14a"],["span.small","HEB"],"mighty man."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.15a","order":"02.19.016.33714"},["b","15a"],["span.small","OR"],"cast my strength."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.19a","order":"02.19.016.33716"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heaven"},"TG Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.20a","order":"02.19.016.33718"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/21.3.1-3"},"Job 21:3 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/16.22a","order":"02.19.016.33720"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death"},"TG Death"],"."]]}
